item.title: Projects
item.description: -- -- MyDoc MyDoc is a SaaS platform, It’s a tool for building telemedical platform on top of the existing flow, that would enable healthcare providers to simplify and accelerate all types of communication, to reduce costs of provided services and much more. Features: Symptom Checker, Health History Management, AI Based Diagnosis, Medical Document Sharing, Text/Video/Audio Chat Built using: Go, Node.js, VueJS, Vuex, Nuxt, Postgres, Docker, Micro-services
